{"tid":1593294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請連登手足及歌藝高手，作歌曲「唱衰林鄭」！","createTime":"2019-09-25T04:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T07:55:11.000Z","uid":302165,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ec5d9f2b8fdb14608aa03470f1037a53313662f6","tid":1593294,"uid":302165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:10:16.000Z","msg":"自2014年上半年俄羅斯介入克裡米亞事務後這首歌在烏克蘭國內多地傳唱，相關消息也為許多國際媒體所報導。<br />\n<br />\n在烏克蘭失去克理米亞之後，烏克蘭民眾針對俄羅斯領導人普京的一句髒話，同時也代表一首歌曲，這首歌唱衰普京：普京傻屄（烏克蘭語：Путiн - хуйло，俄語：Путин - хуйло，IPA： ['putʲɪn xʊj'lo]），或普京是個傻子、普京是白癡。<br />\n參閱：<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/普京傻屄\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC%E5%82%BB%E5%B1%84&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9CZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=7dcf1a8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/普京傻屄</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人的歌「願榮光歸香港」為抗爭振發士氣，使全球觸目，國際動容！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再接再厲，針對林鄭管治無方，賣港喪權，請連登手足及歌藝高手，作歌曲「唱衰林鄭」！<br />\n<br />\n這請大家幫手，推動成事！"},{"pid":"8e6772fccdee185046817ccbfb9168af35202a08","tid":1593294,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"c8767f2500cdf91c7691ba3d4d78418833418330","tid":1593294,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:12:40.000Z","msg":"[文宣] 我哋好似忘記咗其中一條重要戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592692</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dfc3a63a62ea7c8c36cc7cb117cba58059ddb48f","tid":1593294,"uid":302165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e6772fccdee185046817ccbfb9168af35202a08","tid":1593294,"uid":47605,